name: Omg they stealing parking lot!
description:
Omg! Thiefs are stealing the parking lot! Of course with all of the cars inside! Why? Who knows… maybe they're tired of stealing cars one by one, maybe they're doing it just for fun…
Make sure they keep most of the cars inside and not lose all of them in the process!

3 levels

made for 4th alakajam. Entry https://alakajam.com/4th-alakajam/380/omg-they-stealing-parking-lot/
